e-mail: <promed@usa.healthnet.org>
[Confirmation by serology may take 10-14 days (the time it takes to obtain
a second, early convalescent-phase, serum) but virus isolation can be done
in less than that. In such epidemiologically crucial situations, one may
have to be satisfied with "presumptive" diagnoses until such time as second
sera can be obtained and confirmations made. The situation in Venezuela
sounds critical. - Mod.CHC
